*מקמה  -  מקומה   - מקם  -  מקום / mâqôm  mâqôm  meqômâh  meqômâh / (1,2) maw-kome', (3,4) mek-o-mah'
=== Etymology ===

From  [[קוּם]] {{HH|6965}}; properly a standing, that is, a spot; but used widely of a locality (generally or specifically); also (figuratively) of a condition (of body or mind): 
=== Noun ===
[[country]], X home, X open, [[place]], room, space, X whither [-soever].